platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: 天氣預報中盡賞城市風景
在城市風景中一覽天氣資訊

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: An elegant blend of striking photography and nuanced information, Yahoo’s interactive weather app will delight you every time you open it. Expanding the wonderfully streamlined interface reveals a 10-day forecast, heat and wind maps, and other handy displays, while a quick swipe lets you instantly check the temperature in another favorite location.
